name: TC_07_01_01 | Verify the user can search articles in the Help Center with random characters
description: To verify the user gets alert-message when searches in the Help Center with random characters.
descriptionHtml: To verify the user gets alert-message when searches in the Help Center with random characters.

testStage.description: To verify the user gets alert-message when searches in the Help Center with random characters.

steps.name: Preconditions: Login as a registered user
Verify the user is redirected to help center page.
Verify the user gets popup alert-message and empty list after input.
Verify the user redirects to search page and gets alert-message.
